snippet.title: Inside Titanfall: Official Behind the Scenes Video
snippet.description: Prepare for Titanfall! Get an inside look at Titanfall from the team at Respawn Entertainment. Featured in the EA E3 Press Conference. For more information on the game, please visit www.titanfall.com, follow on Twitter at www.twitter.com/titanfallgame or Facebook at www.facebook.com/titanfallgame.
